    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2048年，你将作为一名年轻侦探在陌生城市展开冒险，穿行于广阔的赛博朋克开放世界，空降霓虹灯背后的颓败贫民窟，深入潜藏致命阴谋的奢华豪宅，来寻找一切可能帮助破获命案的关键证据和证人。记忆苏醒，迷雾拨开，找出被夜色掩盖的真相。这座城市的灵感来自重庆洪崖洞和香港九龙城寨，迷宫般错综复杂的建筑层层叠叠，带给你独特的体验和随处可见的隐秘角落。每一个选择都是命运的抉择，它或许会让你靠近真相，或者将你推入更深的黑暗，直至再无回头之路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015470/extras/4d0e407a3ddb348121798445117297a8.webp?t=1731696836\" width=630 height=4 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是Kurt，一名经验丰富的侦探。深夜被派遣调查一起发生在富豪之女身上的命案，在巨大的城市夜幕中穿梭以求侦破命案真相。事实背后的黑暗比你想象的更深，而你的每一步，都将揭开更多令人不安的秘密。真相是否得以昭雪，这座城市的人们即将面对怎样的转变？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015470/extras/4d0e407a3ddb348121798445117297a8.webp?t=1731696836\" width=630 height=4 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015470/extras/5fefa4b922497d5acffa57fa99e2a6fa.webp?t=1731696836\" width=384 height=37 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015470/extras/fef2ff94d82f1fb99a0356d0a8c4e85a.poster.avif?t=1731696836\" width=630 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015470/extras/fef2ff94d82f1fb99a0356d0a8c4e85a.webm?t=1731696836\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015470/extras/fef2ff94d82f1fb99a0356d0a8c4e85a.mp4?t=1731696836\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >霓虹灯下的无数角落里都隐藏着秘密。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >进入高耸入云金碧辉煌的豪楼游览，还是去往电线杆背后破烂陈旧的棚户区探险？你是来去自由的侦探，你说了算。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015470/extras/4d0e407a3ddb348121798445117297a8.webp?t=1731696836\" width=630 height=4 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015470/extras/22da74b33c83603134773ae9df1f924e.webp?t=1731696836\" width=384 height=37 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015470/extras/348384fcc53301c620a714cdb6a2e72e.poster.avif?t=1731696836\" width=630 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015470/extras/348384fcc53301c620a714cdb6a2e72e.webm?t=1731696836\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015470/extras/348384fcc53301c620a714cdb6a2e72e.mp4?t=1731696836\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为侦探Kurt，调查这座城市最有权势人物女儿的谋杀案。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >获得更多关键信息后，再一次探索记忆中的场景，往日重现，你会拾起当初未曾注意的秘密吗？</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过与同事和城市居民的互动，获取提示。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015470/extras/4d0e407a3ddb348121798445117297a8.webp?t=1731696836\" width=630 height=4 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015470/extras/fe275841586283b5a440f95e2896050f.webp?t=1731696836\" width=384 height=37 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015470/extras/81062e280aa55370a1a2c5bc2e4491d3.poster.avif?t=1731696836\" width=630 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015470/extras/81062e280aa55370a1a2c5bc2e4491d3.webm?t=1731696836\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015470/extras/81062e280aa55370a1a2c5bc2e4491d3.mp4?t=1731696836\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与谋杀案件相关的角色互动，揭开他们的谎言，拼凑出真相。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不光是主角会随着故事的发展而成长，NPC也有属于自己的故事。除了主线剧情之外，还有无数支线任务等你完成。更错综离奇的线索，更触动人心的小人物，等你来发现。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015470/extras/4d0e407a3ddb348121798445117297a8.webp?t=1731696836\" width=630 height=4 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015470/extras/f0ad38e6d99c8a0f88f5862ea4912601.webp?t=1731696836\" width=384 height=37 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015470/extras/fe41227370e1411a20348f42798917c0.poster.avif?t=1731696836\" width=630 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015470/extras/fe41227370e1411a20348f42798917c0.webm?t=1731696836\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015470/extras/fe41227370e1411a20348f42798917c0.mp4?t=1731696836\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用游戏内的控制面板分析线索，得出结论！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >现实与直觉的连接，处处堆满了灵光一现的快感。脑洞大开吧！不试试你怎么知道呢！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >要正面对抗邪恶吗？如何在两难中贯彻自己的信念？试图解救他人时，也是为了拯救自己。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015470/extras/4d0e407a3ddb348121798445117297a8.webp?t=1731696836\" width=630 height=4 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015470/extras/18309f3e2be3fe51e818eb1e06035867.webp?t=1731696836\" width=384 height=37 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015470/extras/a39e23e8119465640c2ab1a27beb8835.poster.avif?t=1731696836\" width=630 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015470/extras/a39e23e8119465640c2ab1a27beb8835.webm?t=1731696836\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015470/extras/a39e23e8119465640c2ab1a27beb8835.mp4?t=1731696836\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >感觉压力山大？不妨休息一下，尽情享受美味火锅，或在热闹的夜市中漫游，享受难忘的时光！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >畅玩各种轻松的迷你游戏，收集勋章以换取礼物！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015470/extras/4d0e407a3ddb348121798445117297a8.webp?t=1731696836\" width=630 height=4 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的选择将引领你走向救赎，还是更深的黑暗？</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你会与邪恶硬碰硬吗？</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >视而不见是否意味着你们同流合污？</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >加入我们，踏上这段激动人心的旅程，决策权在你手中。</p></li></ul>",
